<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ج ن د:</span> <span class="c2">(الْجُنْدُ)</span> الْأَعْوَانُ وَالْأَنْصَارُ وَفُلَانٌ <span class="c2">(جَنَّدَ الْجُنُودَ تَجْنِيدًا)</span> وَفِي الْحَدِيثِ: <span class="c2">«الْأَرْوَاحُ جُنُودٌ مُجَنَّدَةٌ»</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>